casebody.data:
Tracey L. VIZZONI, as Executrix of the Estate of Judith A. Schrope, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Barbara MULFORD-DERA, et al., Defendants. M-304 September Term 2018
M-305 September Term 2018
081520 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the miscellaneous motion to impound plaintiff's confidential Appellate Division appendix (M-304) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal (M-305) is granted and the matter is summarily remanded to the Superior Court, Appellate Division to consider on the merits.
